    ('cat_balance_stepping_stones', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for progressive balance play', 'Gonge River Stones', 'Gonge', 'Educational Toys', 'https://www.educationaltoys.co.uk/collections/balance/products/rainbow-river-stone', NULL, '£159.99', 'in_stock', '3+', 'Set of multi-coloured, triangular stepping stones with varying heights and slopes for balance and coordination.', 'These Gonge River Stones offer a dynamic and engaging balance challenge, perfect for 34-36 month olds who are ready for more planned and rule-based movement. The varying heights encourage judging distances and safe practice. Skip if space is limited or child prefers less structured play.', 'The varying heights and slopes of the stones provide a sequenced balance challenge, aligning with the stage shift note for 34-36 months. It encourages deliberate movement and spatial awareness.', 'Requires a reasonable amount of space for effective play. Higher price point.', 'buy', true, 'Excellent gift for active families with space for indoor or outdoor play.', 'Durable and long-lasting, good for multiple children or resale.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.educationaltoys.co.uk/collections/balance/products/rainbow-river-stone', 'https://www.gonge.com/products/river-stones']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_balance_stepping_stones', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for open-ended creative movement', 'Stapelstein Stepping Stones 6+1 Set - Rainbow', 'Stapelstein', 'Scandiborn', 'https://www.scandiborn.co.uk/products/stapelstein-stepping-stones-rainbow-6-1-set', NULL, '£184.95', 'in_stock', '1+', 'Set of seven versatile, lightweight, and colourful stacking stones for balancing, building, and imaginative play.', 'Stapelstein stones are fantastic for fostering creativity alongside physical development. Their open-ended nature allows 34-36 month olds to design their own balance paths and challenges, promoting planned movement and problem-solving. Consider borrowing if unsure about long-term engagement.', 'The modular design allows for creating varied and sequenced balance challenges, directly addressing the stage shift note. They support both physical and cognitive development through open-ended play.', 'Premium price point. Some children may prefer more structured activities.', 'buy', true, 'A highly versatile and durable gift that grows with the child.', 'Excellent for resale due to high demand and durability.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.scandiborn.co.uk/products/stapelstein-stepping-stones-rainbow-6-1-set', 'https://thekidcollective.co.uk/collections/stapelstein']::text[], 'none'),
