    ('cat_balance_stepping_stones', 5, 5, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for tactile sensory exploration', 'Gonge Tactile River Stones - Pk 5', 'Gonge', 'EE-Supplies', 'https://ee-supplies.co.uk/products/gonge-tactile-river-stones-pk-5', NULL, '£100.98', 'in_stock', '3+', 'Set of five river stones with varying tactile surfaces to stimulate sensory perception and balance.', 'These Gonge Tactile River Stones add a sensory dimension to balance play, making them engaging for 34-36 month olds. The different textures provide additional stimulation while children navigate the path, enhancing both balance and tactile discrimination. A good choice for children who benefit from multi-sensory input.', 'Combines balance challenge with sensory input, offering a richer experience for planned movement and exploration. The varied textures add a new layer to the stage-specific balance behaviour.', 'Higher price point. Some children may not be as interested in the tactile aspect.', 'buy', true, 'A unique gift that supports both physical and sensory development.', 'Durable and easy to clean, suitable for long-term use.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://ee-supplies.co.uk/products/gonge-tactile-river-stones-pk-5', 'https://www.gonge.com/products/river-stones']::text[], 'none'),
