    ('cat_threading_beads', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for developing dexterity and concentration', 'Bigjigs Toys Crate of Lacing Beads - 3 Years +', 'Bigjigs Toys', 'Amazon UK', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Bigjigs-Toys-Lacing-Beads-Laces/dp/B004X9W854', NULL, '£18.99', 'in_stock', '3+ years', 'A wooden crate with 90 colourful beads and 5 laces for threading, sorting, and fine motor skill development.', 'This classic set offers chunky wooden beads perfect for developing the precise hand movements needed at this stage. The variety of shapes and colours encourages sorting and pattern-making, building on earlier matching skills. Ideal for sustained concentration and dexterity.', 'Explicitly designed for 3+ years, the large beads are safe and engaging for refining fine motor skills. The open-ended nature supports creativity and cognitive development beyond basic threading.', 'Ensure supervision to prevent younger siblings from accessing small parts, although the beads are chunky.', 'buy', true, 'A well-regarded educational toy that makes a thoughtful and practical gift for a nearly three-year-old.', 'The wooden crate provides convenient storage, helping to keep all pieces together.', 'Conforms to EN71 safety standards. Use under adult supervision.', 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.amazon.co.uk/Bigjigs-Toys-Lacing-Beads-Laces/dp/B004X9W854']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_threading_beads', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for first lacing and fine motor practice', 'Melissa & Doug Primary Lacing Beads', 'Melissa & Doug', 'Argos', 'https://www.argos.co.uk/product/7519288', NULL, '£7.50', 'in_stock', '3+ years', 'A set of 30 brightly coloured wooden beads in various shapes with 2 laces and a storage case.', 'Melissa & Doug is a trusted brand for educational toys. These primary lacing beads are chunky and easy for little hands to grasp, making them ideal for a child''s first foray into more complex threading. The different shapes add an extra layer of cognitive engagement.', 'The explicit 3+ age marking and chunky design align perfectly with the stage shift towards more controlled fine motor activities. The simplicity allows for focus on the threading action itself.', 'Fewer beads than some other sets, but sufficient for initial learning.', 'buy', true, 'A classic and reliable gift that supports early learning and fine motor development.', 'The included storage case is a practical feature for keeping the set tidy.', 'Suitable for ages 3+. Adult supervision recommended.', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.argos.co.uk/product/7519288']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_threading_beads', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for developing shape and number recognition', 'Stringing Solids', 'Early Years Resources', 'Early Years Resources', 'https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/stringing-solids/', NULL, '£30.00', 'in_stock', '3 years +', '100 x 2.5cm beads in 5 different shapes with 10 x 1m cords and activity cards.', 'This set provides a large quantity of chunky beads in various geometric shapes, encouraging both threading and early mathematical concepts like sorting and sequencing. The activity cards offer structured play, guiding children in creating patterns and understanding spatial relationships.', 'The explicit 3+ age marking and focus on diverse shapes and activity cards support the cognitive and fine motor development expected at this stage, moving beyond simple threading to more complex tasks.', 'The price is higher than some other sets, but the quantity and educational value justify it for a comprehensive learning experience.', 'buy', true, 'An excellent educational gift for a child ready to explore shapes, numbers, and patterns through hands-on play.', 'Supplied in a storage jar, making it easy to keep the numerous pieces organised.', 'Suitable for ages 3+. Adult supervision recommended.', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/stringing-solids/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_threading_beads', 4, 4, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for imaginative play and fine motor skills', 'tickit Lacing Fruit Set', 'tickit', 'Early Years Resources', 'https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/tickit-lacing-fruit-set/', NULL, '£34.19', 'in_stock', '3 years+', '21 colourful fruit pieces with hand-painted details and 3 laces with wooden threaders and stops for lacing activities.', 'This lacing fruit set combines fine motor practice with imaginative play, allowing children to create ''fruit kebabs'' while developing dexterity. The chunky, hand-painted pieces are appealing and encourage discussions about healthy eating, making it a versatile toy for this age.', 'The 3+ age marking and chunky pieces are appropriate for the stage. The blend of lacing with imaginative play provides a rich developmental experience, supporting both physical and cognitive skills.', 'While excellent for lacing, it''s not a traditional ''bead'' set, but fits the broader ''chunky lacing'' category.', 'buy', true, 'A delightful and engaging gift that promotes both fine motor skills and creative play.', 'The pieces are durable and easy to clean, ensuring long-lasting play.', 'Suitable for ages 3+. Conforms to relevant safety standards.', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/tickit-lacing-fruit-set/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_threading_beads', 5, 5, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for developing practical life skills', 'Tie-Up Shoe', 'Early Years Resources', 'Early Years Resources', 'https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/tie-up-shoe/', NULL, '£13.00', 'in_stock', '3+ years', 'A wooden shoe designed for practicing lacing and tying shoelaces, promoting independence.', 'This simple yet effective lacing shoe is perfect for children at this stage who are keen to develop practical life skills. It directly supports the ''dressing hands'' aspect of the cluster, helping children master the intricate movements required for tying laces, a key milestone around age three.', 'Explicitly 3+ years, this toy directly addresses a practical fine motor skill that is highly relevant for this age band. It provides a focused activity for developing hand-eye coordination and independence.', 'While excellent for lacing, it''s a single-purpose item and may not offer the same variety as a bead set.', 'buy', true, 'A thoughtful and practical gift that supports a child''s growing independence and fine motor skills.', 'Durable wooden construction ensures it can withstand repeated use.', 'Suitable for ages 3+. Adult supervision recommended.', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/tie-up-shoe/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_threading_beads', 6, 6, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for budgets', 'Lacing Apple', 'Early Years Resources', NULL, 'https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/lacing-apple/', NULL, '£5.52', NULL, NULL, 'Early Years Resources — Lacing Apple', 'Age 3+ years. Lacing activity, suitable for fine motor skills.', 'Age 3+ years. Lacing activity, suitable for fine motor skills.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
